	<ThingDef ParentName="BaseHumanGun">
		<defName>Gun_VolksturmVG1-5_PA</defName>
		<label>Volksturm VG 1-5</label>
		<description> The Volksturm VG 1-5 is an ancient pattern of submachine guns developed in Nazi Germany(Earth's Country back then) and used closer to the end of the war as a last-ditch attempt of manufacturing cheap semi-automatic SMG's in large quantinities. The design did little to help germany, but, unsurprisingly, became quite handy on Rimworlds. </description>
		<graphicData>
		<texPath>Things/Item/Gun_SMG_VolksturmVG1-5</texPath>
		<graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
		</graphicData>
